results.name: Number of 4-ary Lyndon words of length n over GF(4) with trace 1 and subtrace 0.
comment: Let x = RootOf( z^2+z+1 ) and y = 1+x. Also the number of 4-ary Lyndon words of length n over GF(4) with trace x and subtrace 0. Also the number of 4-ary Lyndon words of length n over GF(4) with trace y and subtrace 0.
link: F. Ruskey, 4-ary Lyndon words with given trace and subtrace over GF(4)
results.author: _Frank Ruskey_ and Nate Kube, Aug 23 2002
